                        "description": "<strong>7. Étape 7 - ANNEXES : Photos 1/2</strong><div class=\"step-images count-5\"><figure><img alt=\"Guidoche Sacoche guidon v lo-sac bandouill re 1.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://wiki.lowtechlab.org/images/thumb/e/ee/Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_1.jpg/800px-Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_1.jpg\"/></figure><figure><img alt=\"Guidoche Sacoche guidon v lo-sac bandouill re 2.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://wiki.lowtechlab.org/images/thumb/8/87/Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_2.jpg/800px-Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_2.jpg\"/></figure><figure><img alt=\"Guidoche Sacoche guidon v lo-sac bandouill re 3.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://wiki.lowtechlab.org/images/thumb/b/bd/Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_3.jpg/800px-Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_3.jpg\"/></figure><figure><img alt=\"Guidoche Sacoche guidon v lo-sac bandouill re 4.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://wiki.lowtechlab.org/images/thumb/9/9e/Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_4.jpg/800px-Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_4.jpg\"/></figure><figure><img alt=\"Guidoche Sacoche guidon v lo-sac bandouill re 5.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://wiki.lowtechlab.org/images/thumb/7/7d/Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_5.jpg/800px-Guidoche_Sacoche_guidon_v_lo-sac_bandouill_re_5.jpg\"/></figure></div>",
